Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.66,0:00:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在最讨厌与最喜欢的距离中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.68,0:00:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往往是推理与悬疑的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.50,0:00:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一个漂亮的山水花园中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.39,0:00:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然发生了诡异的杀人凶案
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.37,0:00:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的是一个外表看似小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.91,0:00:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧却过于常人的名侦探柯南
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.28,0:01:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是谢谢你的招待
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.38,0:01:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里果然不愧是号称业界第一的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.11,0:02:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木山家具的社长家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.22,0:02:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是院子就跟别人不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.59,0:02:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是第一次看到有瀑布的院子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.12,0:02:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了就让人感觉心情平静多了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.77,0:02:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.07,0:02:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.94,0:02:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你们都这么喜欢这个院子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.13,0:02:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带你们来到寒舍就算是值得了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.31,0:02:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想差不多就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.28,0:02:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.15,0:02:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.84,0:02:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你们看了就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.57,0:02:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南你快看那里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.62,0:02:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瀑布的水开始满出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.32,0:02:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.45,0:02:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满出来的水都淹到院子里了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.27,0:02:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.86,0:02:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们一定吓了一跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.75,0:02:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当初设计的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.92,0:02:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就设定了每到早晚八点跟下午四点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.54,0:02:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会让瀑布的水流到院子的装置
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.72,0:02:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是水流到院子里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.26,0:02:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会把沙子的摆设打乱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.94,0:03:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的水势不至于让沙子弄乱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.63,0:03:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,30分钟后就会自动排出去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.25,0:03:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是前一任社长设计的山水
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.94,0:03:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家看到后都评价不错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.13,0:03:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.85,0:03:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有点工作要做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.67,0:03:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到晚餐的时候我们再好好聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.46,0:03:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至于车子你就不用去担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.91,0:03:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我会让秘书帮您开过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都让您费心真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.64,0:03:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人有困难就应该互相帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.41,0:03:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 凌佳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.77,0:03:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好好招呼他们哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.11,0:03:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长 我一定会的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.67,0:03:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个设计还真是不错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.13,0:03:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.18,0:03:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人哪会知道维持这些东西要花多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.81,0:03:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山木那个家伙设计的这个什么山水根本就是花钱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.64,0:03:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南你看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.35,0:03:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些白沙被水冲出的纹路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.51,0:03:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透过水看得好清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:03:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮哦 小兰姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了晚上如果映着月亮一定很浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.90,0:04:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个景致真的没话说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.06,0:04:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长有不少客户
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就专门会挑满月的时候到家里来玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝杯水酒配上富士山跟满月啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太痛快了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.43,0:04:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.21,0:04:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是柱子上面吊的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是取物竿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.13,0:04:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取物竿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.57,0:04:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有什么东西掉在院子里的白沙上的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.57,0:04:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就得用到这根取物竿了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.56,0:04:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则不就把白沙那么漂亮的纹路给破坏掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.67,0:04:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.69,0:04:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,设计的人还真是会想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为换了马岛社长之后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.21,0:04:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庭院设计师一个月只会来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就得小心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.23,0:05:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始排水了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.83,0:05:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.31,0:05:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,设计的还真是不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.72,0:05:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水流石庭的玄机（前篇）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.36,0:05:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位如果腻了就请到客厅去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.26,0:05:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经为大家准备了饭前酒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等的就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.82,0:05:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 你说你没钱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.97,0:05:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你当我三岁小孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.67,0:05:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差500万
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.91,0:05:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 加上利息是700万
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.33,0:05:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马岛社长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.22,0:05:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最好在这个月里把钱凑齐了还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.59,0:05:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然就开除你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听清楚了没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:05:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下 社长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这栋别墅真是够壮观的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.95,0:06:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 请进屋去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.68,0:06:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.75,0:06:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三位请这边坐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.24,0:06:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是刚才那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.93,0:06:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这就去拿点饮料过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.06,0:06:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以给我一瓶啤酒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.97,0:06:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.56,0:06:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么白天就喝酒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.02,0:06:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.73,0:06:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凌佳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.45,0:06:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人是干什么的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.49,0:06:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们三位是马岛社长的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.86,0:06:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.57,0:07:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我们不是什么往来的客户
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.22,0:07:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是到了三本坡那里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到汽油刚好用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.39,0:07:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马岛社长又刚好经过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.23,0:07:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这才和马岛社长认识的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.35,0:07:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏社长人很亲切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还邀请我们到他府上来晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.62,0:07:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么平易近人的社长还真是不多见哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只会陌生人面前摆出一副好脸色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.19,0:07:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这个样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.98,0:07:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是纪念木山家具一号店成立的晚餐会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.14,0:07:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与会的应该都是我们自己人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.54,0:07:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系来 远藤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.86,0:07:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马岛社长既然邀请他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.08,0:07:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说吃饭的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.39,0:07:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多几个人 也比较香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是没错啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.64,0:07:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来介绍一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是社长秘书
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桥本政之先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.44,0:07:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.15,0:07:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至于这位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.32,0:08:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,则是关系企业木山室内家饰的社长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.52,0:08:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远藤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.03,0:08:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远藤社长以前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.40,0:08:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箭术高明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.51,0:08:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还曾经代表国家参赛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.02,0:08:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可真是了不得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.96,0:08:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.16,0:08:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是好久以前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.90,0:08:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在早就生疏了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.79,0:08:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至于我自己呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.12,0:08:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫木山智则是一个自由作家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.63,0:08:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你就是写非洲漫游之旅的那个木山先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.30,0:08:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.13,0:08:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兰姐姐 你认识他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.76,0:08:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他曾经到很多国家旅行写了不少书呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.98,0:08:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是看过你写的非洲漫游之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.69,0:08:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.69,0:08:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.39,0:08:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太感动了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.97,0:08:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方便的话可以跟你要个签名吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.14,0:08:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.26,0:08:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这次要办一个摄影展
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.27,0:08:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是门票
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.33,0:08:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你来赏光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:08:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要送我门票啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.58,0:09:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.96,0:09:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我这就帮你签名
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.49,0:09:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这支钢笔好像很旧的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.25,0:09:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是家父的遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是有名的牌子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.96,0:09:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我就是舍不得丢掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.68,0:09:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才会一直带在身上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.80,0:09:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 这就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.43,0:09:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以请你的朋友一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.68,0:09:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我一定会去参观的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.16,0:09:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你竟然跟木山家具也有渊源
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点我还真的不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.00,0:09:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家公司就是由我父亲创建的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.94,0:09:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我父亲死后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.44,0:09:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马岛社长才接了他的位子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们去看过山水了没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.68,0:09:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看过了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那片白沙的纹路实在太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.22,0:09:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.42,0:09:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那片白沙和瀑布
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.24,0:09:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我父亲 趁着忙碌的空档
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:09:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点一滴用心打造完成的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:10:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 智则哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.36,0:10:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸是怎么死掉的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.79,0:10:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 这样问不礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.52,0:10:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是去年车祸死的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.53,0:10:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.10,0:10:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是很难预料的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.14,0:10:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面有个地方看到的夜景很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.26,0:10:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待会一起去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.03,0:10:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保证你们不会失望的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.76,0:10:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.22,0:10:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们去吧 柯南
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.72,0:10:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话你们去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.05,0:10:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真要我选的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.95,0:10:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我宁可坐在这里喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.09,0:10:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 爸爸就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我劝你还是看看的好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保证你看了不会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里和东京不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.07,0:10:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星星特别近好像真的要掉下来一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.30,0:10:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星星啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.11,0:10:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.41,0:10:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拿这么多杯太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:11:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您也可以试试啤酒以外的酒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.32,0:11:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我待会再为您端过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.20,0:11:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.25,0:11:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就放心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.96,0:11:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先喝这个好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.76,0:11:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸你不要这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.30,0:11:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.26,0:11:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法要流出来了 这很浪费的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.52,0:11:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一碰到酒他就没分寸了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 再来一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.71,0:11:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就恭敬不如从命了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.54,0:11:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行行行 这就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.37,0:11:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失陪一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.81,0:11:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马岛社长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.83,0:12:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.62,0:12:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说我最近要办一个摄影展
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不嫌弃的话就请去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摄影展啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.23,0:12:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不出你这小子挺努力的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.91,0:12:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会抽空去看的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是上个月的营收报告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.37,0:12:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的数字应该不会让我看不下去才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.04,0:12:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.78,0:12:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长 我已经把晚餐准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.35,0:12:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就请各位去餐厅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.89,0:12:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 等了这么久 终于可以吃晚餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.00,0:13:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望我们木山家具的生意能够蒸蒸日上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.20,0:13:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个肉好好吃哦 小兰姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.01,0:13:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 好软哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.99,0:13:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 再喝一杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.49,0:13:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 真是不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到你那么喜欢那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.78,0:13:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是难得的缘分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.48,0:13:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就把它便宜让你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.58,0:13:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您真爱开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.61,0:13:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看你跟你爸爸好好商量之后再决定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.63,0:14:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么各位请慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.70,0:14:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有点公事需要去处理一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.02,0:14:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.96,0:14:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.99,0:14:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想看一卷录影带
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.34,0:14:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待会再去看夜景好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.34,0:14:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们随时都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.40,0:14:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在11点15分左右去接你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.15,0:14:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在房间等就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.06,0:14:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会是什么录影带啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是他崇拜的一个冒险家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫什么关口博之的纪录片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.88,0:14:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又一次碰巧发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把它带过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.19,0:14:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.35,0:14:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么冒险家的纪录片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.38,0:14:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为他沉迷那种玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.50,0:14:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公司才会被马岛那种人给抢走的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.78,0:14:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桥本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.86,0:14:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的是什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.30,0:14:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马岛社长不是你说的那种人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.64,0:15:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远藤先生你怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.04,0:15:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会为马岛说话太阳打西边出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你现在帮他说话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.90,0:15:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也无济于事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.41,0:15:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是要你为业绩不佳负责
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.29,0:15:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下个月就要请你走路了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.76,0:15:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过木山室内家饰的赤字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.13,0:15:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本就是母公司木山家具逼你制造出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.50,0:15:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得你之前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.47,0:15:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还把这股气随便迁怒在旁人身上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.60,0:15:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直嚷着“为什么叫我走路”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.75,0:15:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实大家都很担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.98,0:15:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深怕你那样有一天会把马岛给杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.91,0:15:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你够了没有 桥本
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.24,0:15:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的要生气了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.45,0:15:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.39,0:15:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也必须要告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公司还有工作等着处理
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.87,0:15:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.19,0:15:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是算了比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.34,0:15:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的是什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.80,0:16:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那张桌子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.55,0:16:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起初看他是个好好先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.45,0:16:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦咬住就会死缠不放
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.65,0:16:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是马岛一贯的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我劝你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.31,0:16:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不要跟他有任何牵扯比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.87,0:16:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桥本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.27,0:16:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.63,0:16:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看我们也早点回去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.93,0:16:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们就多坐一会 有什么关系呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人啊 明天会怎么样都很难说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.83,0:16:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能喝的时候就要及时行乐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.64,0:16:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您这话说得太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.96,0:16:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 你不要喝了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.67,0:16:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经这么晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.09,0:17:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生我看我们就喝到这里结束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.59,0:17:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸 起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.84,0:17:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸 回房间去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一瓶酒没喝完
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.90,0:17:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生得意须尽欢嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.35,0:17:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生你不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.28,0:17:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰到大家了真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还可以喝好几杯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.50,0:17:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把这个拿去 它治疗宿醉很有效
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.45,0:17:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.99,0:17:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有什么事我都在这
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.71,0:17:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随时叫我一声就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.43,0:17:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.94,0:17:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们早点睡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你走一直线嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.27,0:17:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.97,0:17:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.33,0:17:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.95,0:17:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他喝成这样都要怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.32,0:17:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不该让你爸爸喝这么多酒的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.52,0:17:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您就别放在心上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.93,0:17:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到哪里都是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.69,0:18:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是谢谢您帮我把他扶上来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.23,0:18:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请早点休息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.74,0:18:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.52,0:18:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.47,0:18:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 让你们久等了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.16,0:18:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你千万别这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.18,0:18:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,录影带好看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.22,0:18:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.24,0:18:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那支纪录片真的非常有临场感
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.44,0:18:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这就要去遥望山那里看看了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.55,0:18:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上请小心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:18:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.16,0:18:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就像做梦一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.61,0:19:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是毛利叔叔也来看看就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.57,0:19:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真叫人怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.28,0:19:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我小的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.42,0:19:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常跟我爸一起来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.57,0:19:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸以前也很喜欢这里的夜景
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.97,0:19:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.39,0:19:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里的夜景还好看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.09,0:19:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个美景真是叫人感动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.63,0:19:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 柯南
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.53,0:19:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们喜欢就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.89,0:19:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们先去睡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.80,0:19:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.85,0:19:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凌佳姐晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.36,0:19:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好睡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.08,0:20:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.21,0:20:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很谢谢你带我们去看夜景
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你们这么喜欢就值得了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.75,0:20:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.37,0:20:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你早点休息哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.71,0:20:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么声音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.45,0:20:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.07,0:20:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凌佳姐姐 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.88,0:21:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.00,0:21:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.28,0:21:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马岛社长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.41,0:21:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事叫成这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.34,0:21:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马岛社长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.49,0:21:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兰 立刻去打电话报警
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.69,0:21:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.93,0:21:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.19,0:21:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.16,0:21:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能过去这是一起他杀案件
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.61,0:21:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保存现场完整
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.87,0:21:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都不能到院子里去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.84,0:21:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为你是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.53,0:21:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.96,0:21:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下毛利小五郎 是一名侦探
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.17,0:21:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说你就是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.06,0:21:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位名侦探
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.54,0:21:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是在下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.08,0:21:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.27,0:21:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长的遗体好像有点不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.82,0:21:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么地方不对劲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.87,0:22:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的遗体周围 竟然都没有脚印
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.27,0:22:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.17,0:22:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个凶手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.47,0:22:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎么把社长放到那里的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.66,0:23:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有什么拖过的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.73,0:23:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.44,0:23:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果照叔叔的说法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.07,0:23:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗体应该不会那样横躺在这里才对
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.41,0:24:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这么一来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.77,0:24:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.61,0:24:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.13,0:24:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.46,0:24:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.00,0:24:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水流石庭的玄机（后篇）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.61,0:24:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.13,0:24:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排水沟
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.10,0:24:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集是解决篇
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.11,0:24:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 爸爸 犯人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.79,0:24:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没睡觉 还不知道是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.38,0:00:17.73,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop my love for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.83,0:00:27.55,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我俩讨论的未来中必定有你我的归属
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.07,0:00:31.20,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh baby I can't stop my love for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.36,0:00:34.88,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愿意成为你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.48,0:00:42.99,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你我牵紧的手发誓与你共此一生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.05,0:00:49.78,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“我讨厌你”这句话即使是玩笑话我也不忍出口
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.81,0:00:56.87,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“我喜欢你”这句话如果不是事实我也不会说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.54,0:01:05.07,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你在无法见面时没有心思顾及其他一般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.35,0:01:10.80,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心也被你一个人所独占
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.38,0:01:14.83,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop my love for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.85,0:01:24.34,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不让我俩的爱分隔两地请你紧紧拥抱着我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.15,0:01:31.52,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此心绪不宁的夜晚仍会造访
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.52,0:01:39.45,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此时就请你给我一个大大的拥抱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.15,0:22:27.29,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每当清晨来临我便会想起你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.55,0:22:33.22,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时只要在你身边就感到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.81,0:22:39.88,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为恐惧时间的流逝黯然泪下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.17,0:22:45.10,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每每出现在不断改变的人心之中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.84,0:22:58.79,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不抱期待就不会失去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.64,0:23:05.64,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也别因此无欲无求
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.87,0:23:13.01,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论前方是什么样的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.73,0:23:20.05,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在梦醒之后你的人依然在远方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.28,0:23:25.60,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我的心意先一步飘向你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.89,0:23:33.14,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落英缤纷的这条路依旧没有改变
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.46,0:23:38.92,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我依然想挽着你的手漫步其中
